## Summary Table

| Aspect | Details |
|--------|---------|
| **Column Model** | `{id, x, y, width, depth, height, rotation, type, name, showLabel}` |
| **Beam Model** | `{id, startRef: {id, ...}, endRef: {id, ...}, width, depth, floorLevel}` |
| **Beam-Column Link** | Beams store column IDs in `startRef.id` and `endRef.id` |
| **Delete Cascade** | When column deleted: 1) Column removed, 2) Wall attachments detached, 3) **All beams with that column reference are deleted** |
| **Beam Validation** | Beams require BOTH columns to exist and be different to render |
| **Missing Column Behavior** | Beam won't render; `getBeamRenderData` returns null |
| **Selection Delete** | Delete key triggers COLUMN_DELETE action via selectHandler |

